						<div class="postbody">Good point, it's hard to know how to correct the even/odd time. Here's a rewrite that tells whether it's too soon or too late. It tests both enabling BG and disabling BG, though the timings are the same. To get my emulator passing, I had to set the time around PPU clock 339 of scanline 20.
<br />
<br /><a href="http://h1.ripway.com/blargg/temp/10-even_odd_timing.nes.zip" class="postlink">10-even_odd_timing.nes.zip</a>
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"> The readme and source don't seem to indicate any details on the behavior.</div>
<br />Yep, this is just tests, no documentation of correct behavior (beyond what the test should give).</div>

